snippet.title: Cards of Ethernity Teaser
snippet.description:
Cards of Ethernity (CoE) is a digital collectible competitive card play-and-earn game. At its core CoE is a blockchain-based game, enabling users to trade and sell their cards freely, with the same level of ownership as if they were real, tangible cards. 

- Aether Games Website (https://www.aethergames.io/)
- CoE Website (https://coe.gg/)
- GoE Website (https://goe.gg/)
